snippet.title: Attack On Quest VR Titan Fan Game
snippet.description:
This trailer contains footage from the upcoming v0.3.0 public release.

Attack on Quest is a free-to-play VR fan game built for the Oculus Quest. The game can be sideloaded to Quest 1 and 2, or played on PCVR using the links below. Full cross-play multiplayer compatibility is available between Quest and PCVR versions.

Thank you to ac_tomas for assisting with numerous models and textures.
Female titan model, texture painting, and cinematic sequence created by ac_tomas.
Check out his other work:
artstation.com/ornerybrush
instagram.com/ac_tomas_

Quest Version:
https://sidequestvr.com/app/502/attack-on-quest

PCVR Version:
https://aoq.itch.io/attack-on-quest

For news updates, join the Discord:
https://discord.gg/Bgy9Fzu

To support the development of the game, get behind the scenes access and test features before public releases, join us on buymeacoffee:
https://www.buymeacoffee.com/AoQ
